00:19:36.202 --> 00:19:37.401
I'll follow your instructions

00:19:37.401 --> 00:19:38.482
in the future.

00:19:38.641 --> 00:19:40.081
If I must be alone

00:19:40.081 --> 00:19:41.321
with a man,

00:19:41.321 --> 00:19:42.922
I'll maintain proper distance.

00:19:43.442 --> 00:19:44.722
We're different.

00:19:45.242 --> 00:19:47.762
How are we any different?

00:19:49.442 --> 00:19:50.242
It's just...

00:19:53.962 --> 00:19:55.121
Just different.

00:20:00.042 --> 00:20:01.042
Huan Zong,

00:20:01.121 --> 00:20:02.482
I was teasing you.

00:20:02.601 --> 00:20:03.161
We

00:20:03.161 --> 00:20:04.801
are very, very good friends.

00:20:04.841 --> 00:20:06.401
Of course, we can stay together.

00:20:06.561 --> 00:20:07.321
Moreover,

00:20:07.401 --> 00:20:08.561
whenever

00:20:08.561 --> 00:20:09.801
I'm with you,

00:20:09.841 --> 00:20:11.561
I feel completely at ease.

00:20:16.922 --> 00:20:17.841
We

00:20:18.841 --> 00:20:20.601
are just good friends?

00:20:26.522 --> 00:20:27.442
Huan Zong.

00:20:29.482 --> 00:20:30.321
Huan Zong?

00:20:32.282 --> 00:20:34.762
Why is your face so red?

00:20:42.321 --> 00:20:44.442
Are you angry

00:20:44.722 --> 00:20:46.242
because I teased you just now?

00:20:48.242 --> 00:20:48.962
No.

00:20:49.242 --> 00:20:50.002
Then why

00:20:50.002 --> 00:20:51.401
is your face so flushed?

00:20:53.361 --> 00:20:54.881
I won't joke with you anymore,

00:20:54.881 --> 00:20:55.801
is that better?

00:21:11.034 --> 00:21:13.498
(Jiao Tong Pavilion)

00:21:16.202 --> 00:21:16.762
Who's there?

00:21:16.962 --> 00:21:17.641
Show yourself!

00:21:18.401 --> 00:21:19.321
Don't kill me.

00:21:19.561 --> 00:21:20.242
Don't kill me.

00:21:20.881 --> 00:21:22.242
I'm just a servant here.

00:21:27.682 --> 00:21:28.561
I won't kill you.

00:21:29.361 --> 00:21:30.361
What happened here?

00:21:30.561 --> 00:21:31.361
Just now,

00:21:31.482 --> 00:21:32.401
Jiao Tong

00:21:32.401 --> 00:21:33.522
fought with someone.

00:21:33.962 --> 00:21:35.361
His face was terrifying,

00:21:35.762 --> 00:21:37.002
all peeling off.

00:21:37.321 --> 00:21:39.202
I never thought he'd harm people.

00:21:39.401 --> 00:21:40.922
He even took that lady.

00:21:40.962 --> 00:21:41.722
Lady?

00:21:41.962 --> 00:21:42.881
Where was she taken?

00:21:43.401 --> 00:21:45.482
Two young masters

00:21:45.922 --> 00:21:47.161
saved her.

00:21:47.202 --> 00:21:48.121
What about Jiao Tong?

00:21:48.801 --> 00:21:49.522
I don't know.

00:21:49.522 --> 00:21:50.641
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:21:51.081 --> 00:21:52.841
I truly know nothing anyway.

00:21:53.002 --> 00:21:54.962
It was the newly arrived young master

00:21:54.962 --> 00:21:55.841
who let him escape.

00:21:55.881 --> 00:21:56.922
Let him escape?

00:22:11.282 --> 00:22:12.561
Stop pacing.

00:22:12.841 --> 00:22:14.601
Jiao Tong's nothing special.

00:22:14.601 --> 00:22:15.841
Lin Hu can handle him.

00:22:16.442 --> 00:22:18.282
Then why isn't he back yet?

00:22:18.881 --> 00:22:20.081
Sit down for a game.

00:22:20.202 --> 00:22:21.361
Wait for him calmly.

00:22:22.561 --> 00:22:23.282
Fine.

00:22:23.801 --> 00:22:26.002
I'll show you how to lose.

00:22:42.682 --> 00:22:43.801
Your way of playing

00:22:43.801 --> 00:22:45.002
is rather unique.

00:22:45.442 --> 00:22:46.482
Of course.

00:22:50.522 --> 00:22:51.081
Okay.

00:22:51.121 --> 00:22:52.601
Huan Zong, I've won.

00:22:59.282 --> 00:23:00.962
How's this a win?

00:23:01.282 --> 00:23:02.841
One, two, three, four, five.

00:23:02.841 --> 00:23:03.762
Five in a row.

00:23:03.762 --> 00:23:04.922
This means I win.

00:23:05.522 --> 00:23:06.682
Aren't we playing Go?

00:23:06.762 --> 00:23:08.442
You didn't specify earlier.

00:23:12.042 --> 00:23:12.922
Cheating, are you?

00:23:13.081 --> 00:23:14.282
I won't stoop to your level.

00:23:16.242 --> 00:23:17.682
You accuse me of cheating,

00:23:17.722 --> 00:23:18.682
yet you never mentioned

00:23:18.682 --> 00:23:19.601
that I didn't blame you

00:23:19.601 --> 00:23:20.482
for not telling me

00:23:20.482 --> 00:23:21.881
you are Master Writer.

00:23:22.881 --> 00:23:23.522
What's there

00:23:23.522 --> 00:23:24.722
to hide about?

00:23:24.762 --> 00:23:26.482
You are Master Writer,

00:23:26.641 --> 00:23:29.121
such a brilliant storybook writer.

00:23:30.002 --> 00:23:30.922
Brilliant?

00:23:32.002 --> 00:23:33.321
Except for you,

00:23:33.482 --> 00:23:35.242
no one reads my books anyway.

00:23:36.641 --> 00:23:37.641
I get it.

00:23:37.762 --> 00:23:39.321
So you kept it from me

00:23:39.321 --> 00:23:40.641
because no one buys your books,

00:23:40.641 --> 00:23:41.601
and you

00:23:41.722 --> 00:23:42.962
feel ashamed,

00:23:42.962 --> 00:23:43.641
right?

00:23:45.962 --> 00:23:46.682
Young Master.

00:23:48.401 --> 00:23:50.042
Lin Hu, you're back.

00:23:51.641 --> 00:23:52.482
Young Master.

00:23:52.601 --> 00:23:53.722
It has been settled.

00:23:54.002 --> 00:23:54.682
Considering

00:23:54.682 --> 00:23:55.641
we're both foxes,

00:23:55.801 --> 00:23:57.202
please leave its corpse intact.

00:23:57.482 --> 00:23:58.321
Foxes?

00:23:58.401 --> 00:24:00.361
So Lin Hu, you're a demon cultivator?

00:24:00.962 --> 00:24:01.801
What's wrong?

00:24:01.962 --> 00:24:03.522
You won't be like those people

00:24:03.561 --> 00:24:05.161
who would harm demon cultivators, right?

00:24:05.401 --> 00:24:06.682
What did they do?

00:24:06.881 --> 00:24:07.762
Holding prejudice?

00:24:09.282 --> 00:24:10.722
Demon and human cultivators,

00:24:10.722 --> 00:24:11.922
as long as they're righteous,

00:24:11.962 --> 00:24:12.841
to me,

00:24:12.841 --> 00:24:14.042
they're all the same.

00:24:14.202 --> 00:24:15.002
Besides,

00:24:15.042 --> 00:24:16.801
demon cultivation
is extremely difficult.

00:24:16.841 --> 00:24:18.682
So, it's impressive.

00:24:18.841 --> 00:24:19.482
Really?

00:24:20.922 --> 00:24:21.881
Thank you.

00:24:22.161 --> 00:24:22.762
But

00:24:22.881 --> 00:24:24.522
since you're a demon cultivator,

00:24:24.682 --> 00:24:25.601
how did you

00:24:25.601 --> 00:24:26.922
know Huan Zong?

00:24:27.042 --> 00:24:28.922
Isn't Liuguang Sect...

00:24:29.161 --> 00:24:30.242
That's enough.

00:24:30.242 --> 00:24:31.361
Why so many questions?

00:24:31.641 --> 00:24:33.002
Master Zong, I'll take my leave.

00:25:10.962 --> 00:25:12.482
You're truly hideous-looking.

00:25:13.202 --> 00:25:14.161
Who said that?

00:25:35.601 --> 00:25:36.641
How are you improving

00:25:36.641 --> 00:25:37.522
so quickly now?

00:25:39.561 --> 00:25:41.042
You are just too inept.

00:25:42.161 --> 00:25:43.881
You've secretly learned
from Master, right?

00:25:44.081 --> 00:25:44.682
No.

00:25:45.722 --> 00:25:46.801
Then that means

00:25:46.841 --> 00:25:48.242
you found your cultivation partner,

00:25:48.242 --> 00:25:48.742
right?

00:25:48.841 --> 00:25:50.321
It's not that easy to find one.

00:25:50.561 --> 00:25:51.361
I merely

00:25:51.361 --> 00:25:52.881
captured a few female cultivators.

00:25:53.361 --> 00:25:54.841
The dual cultivation

00:25:55.002 --> 00:25:56.321
is actually quite fascinating.

00:25:57.002 --> 00:25:57.641
What?

00:25:58.282 --> 00:25:59.482
Female cultivators?

00:26:00.161 --> 00:26:01.641
What? Angry with me?

00:26:01.682 --> 00:26:03.841
Next time, I'll definitely take you.

00:26:06.401 --> 00:26:07.161
What?

00:26:08.762 --> 00:26:09.801
Female cultivators?

00:26:21.482 --> 00:26:23.081
Actually, what he did wasn't wrong,

00:26:23.081 --> 00:26:23.722
right?

00:26:24.121 --> 00:26:24.762
We've all

00:26:24.762 --> 00:26:26.361
taken human form recently.

00:26:26.641 --> 00:26:27.722
This method

00:26:27.762 --> 00:26:29.042
helps enhance our cultivation.

00:26:29.722 --> 00:26:31.881
I've seen many demon cultivators

00:26:31.881 --> 00:26:32.801
who did the same thing

00:26:32.801 --> 00:26:33.841
to facilitate cultivation.

00:26:34.081 --> 00:26:34.601
I...

00:26:36.161 --> 00:26:38.522
I could do that too, couldn't I?

00:26:44.202 --> 00:26:45.641
Such intense sword energy.

00:27:43.442 --> 00:27:44.682
Why are you copying me?

00:27:46.202 --> 00:27:47.561
I want to be like you.

00:27:49.002 --> 00:27:50.401
You can't be like me.

00:27:50.442 --> 00:27:51.722
You're a demon cultivator.

00:27:52.121 --> 00:27:53.282
What's wrong with that?

00:27:53.321 --> 00:27:54.561
Look down on demon cultivators?

00:27:56.242 --> 00:27:57.762
Even as a demon cultivator,

00:27:57.962 --> 00:27:59.282
you shouldn't casually steal

00:27:59.282 --> 00:28:00.282
others' achievements.

00:28:01.722 --> 00:28:03.401
If you truly want to be like me,

00:28:03.722 --> 00:28:04.881
everything must be achieved

00:28:04.881 --> 00:28:05.881
through your own efforts.

00:28:06.042 --> 00:28:06.801
Understand?

00:28:36.401 --> 00:28:38.401
Lin Hu, where are you?

00:28:38.522 --> 00:28:39.762
Come drink with me.

00:28:43.161 --> 00:28:44.161
Young Master,

00:28:44.601 --> 00:28:45.361
do you have

00:28:45.361 --> 00:28:46.522
anything to say?

00:28:46.841 --> 00:28:47.601
No.

00:28:47.762 --> 00:28:49.641
Just drinking alone
makes me feel lonely.

00:28:49.841 --> 00:28:51.161
I wanted your company.

00:28:53.962 --> 00:28:54.722
I...

00:28:54.722 --> 00:28:55.641
No need to explain.

00:28:55.801 --> 00:28:56.841
I trust you,

00:28:57.242 --> 00:28:59.002
and the cultivation path you've chosen.

00:29:02.881 --> 00:29:04.161
Never mind. Don't come.

00:29:07.522 --> 00:29:09.482
Huan Zong, what are you
doing at this hour?

00:29:11.042 --> 00:29:12.202
Drinking?

00:29:12.401 --> 00:29:14.522
Didn't you say you're fasting
and won't drink?

00:29:15.922 --> 00:29:18.242
Just occasionally.
A small amount won't hurt.

00:29:18.442 --> 00:29:19.762
Then why didn't you invite me?

00:29:19.762 --> 00:29:20.762
I want some too.

00:29:24.841 --> 00:29:26.002
Trust me?

00:29:34.762 --> 00:29:36.081
Useless fool.

00:29:36.242 --> 00:29:37.242
You couldn't even handle

00:29:37.242 --> 00:29:38.121
such a simple task.

00:29:40.682 --> 00:29:42.641
Master, I am incompetent.

00:29:42.801 --> 00:29:44.282
I failed to make proper arrangements.

00:29:44.482 --> 00:29:46.002
But don't worry.

00:29:46.161 --> 00:29:46.881
As long as they

00:29:46.881 --> 00:29:47.841
stay in Yi City,

00:29:47.841 --> 00:29:48.682
they won't escape.

00:29:48.722 --> 00:29:49.682
I humbly request

00:29:49.682 --> 00:29:51.682
that you speak kindly of us
before the Lord.

00:29:52.242 --> 00:29:53.722
Please don't punish us.

00:29:53.962 --> 00:29:54.841
Considering your years

00:29:54.841 --> 00:29:56.762
of devotion to the Lord,

00:29:57.042 --> 00:29:58.641
I'll let this slide.

00:29:58.922 --> 00:30:01.081
But if you fail again...

00:30:01.081 --> 00:30:02.401
I'll accept any punishment.

00:30:14.641 --> 00:30:15.401
Stop.

00:30:17.641 --> 00:30:19.081
You're Jiao Tong?

00:30:19.401 --> 00:30:20.282
Who are you?

00:30:20.641 --> 00:30:22.042
Ling Bo from Zhaohan Sect.

00:30:23.321 --> 00:30:24.561
So you're Lady Ling Bo

00:30:24.561 --> 00:30:25.801
from Zhaohan Sect.

00:30:26.242 --> 00:30:27.361
What do you want from me?

00:30:27.682 --> 00:30:29.202
Why did you capture that lady?

00:30:29.442 --> 00:30:30.401
Lady Ling Bo,

00:30:30.401 --> 00:30:32.321
are you meddling in others' affairs?

00:30:32.801 --> 00:30:34.121
What's this

00:30:34.282 --> 00:30:35.922
got to do with you?

00:30:36.121 --> 00:30:38.042
She belongs to Yunhua Sect.

00:30:38.401 --> 00:30:40.561
How dare you seize someone
from Yunhua Sect?

00:30:40.641 --> 00:30:41.801
What's your real purpose?

00:30:41.922 --> 00:30:42.881
My purpose

00:30:42.881 --> 00:30:44.442
is none of your concern.

00:30:45.282 --> 00:30:47.161
But if you don't leave now,

00:30:47.522 --> 00:30:49.161
even Zhaohan Sect members

00:30:49.801 --> 00:30:51.081
won't be safe from me.

00:30:51.202 --> 00:30:52.202
How dare you!

00:31:00.202 --> 00:31:01.922
I'll come back for you after things

00:31:02.161 --> 00:31:03.242
are settled tomorrow.

00:31:08.361 --> 00:31:09.482
I can't let it go to waste.

00:31:41.682 --> 00:31:42.682
Huan Zong.

00:31:43.841 --> 00:31:45.321
Huan Zong.

00:31:45.522 --> 00:31:46.242
I'm here.

00:31:48.161 --> 00:31:49.242
Actually,

00:31:49.242 --> 00:31:51.522
I've always envied
your bond with Lin Hu.

00:31:51.601 --> 00:31:53.042
You're always together.

00:31:53.321 --> 00:31:55.522
Though he calls you "Young Master",

00:31:55.722 --> 00:31:56.922
I know

00:31:57.042 --> 00:31:59.962
you're truly

00:32:00.202 --> 00:32:01.801
close friends.

00:32:02.401 --> 00:32:04.601
When I was at Yunhua Sect,

00:32:04.601 --> 00:32:06.641
I had close friends too.

00:32:06.801 --> 00:32:09.161
My senior brothers,

00:32:09.161 --> 00:32:10.361
sisters, and I

00:32:10.361 --> 00:32:12.081
were always together

00:32:12.321 --> 00:32:13.841
just like you and Lin Hu.

00:32:13.922 --> 00:32:15.202
I was really happy back then.

00:32:18.601 --> 00:32:20.161
By that logic,

00:32:21.401 --> 00:32:23.282
I should envy you.

00:32:23.762 --> 00:32:25.081
Envy me?

00:32:25.361 --> 00:32:26.482
Why?

00:32:26.601 --> 00:32:28.242
Because you have many friends.

00:32:30.161 --> 00:32:31.161
Unlike me.

00:32:33.962 --> 00:32:35.161
Day and night,

00:32:35.682 --> 00:32:37.881
I trained rigorously with my master.

00:32:38.561 --> 00:32:39.881
Even now,

00:32:40.242 --> 00:32:41.522
I barely have time

00:32:41.522 --> 00:32:43.161
to interact with juniors.

00:32:43.881 --> 00:32:45.042
So Huan Zong,

00:32:45.202 --> 00:32:46.762
were you brought to Liuguang Sect

00:32:46.801 --> 00:32:48.522
when you were very young?

00:32:48.601 --> 00:32:50.321
I was already grown that year.

00:32:50.442 --> 00:32:52.002
But after family troubles,

00:32:52.242 --> 00:32:52.962
my master took me

00:32:52.962 --> 00:32:54.482
to Liuguang Sect.

00:32:57.184 --> 00:33:01.442
♪Time engraves into rings♪

00:33:01.442 --> 00:33:02.601
All these years,

00:33:03.442 --> 00:33:05.121
only Lin Hu stayed by my side.

00:33:05.321 --> 00:33:06.922
So strictly speaking,

00:33:07.682 --> 00:33:08.242
he's my only

00:33:08.242 --> 00:33:09.242
true friend.

00:33:12.841 --> 00:33:14.282
But it's different now.

00:33:14.321 --> 00:33:15.361
I'm your friend too.

00:33:15.601 --> 00:33:18.042
Now, you have two friends.

00:33:20.881 --> 00:33:21.561
Yes.

00:33:22.962 --> 00:33:23.962
Now, there's you too.

00:33:25.922 --> 00:33:26.881
Actually,

00:33:26.881 --> 00:33:28.081
you've always hidden

00:33:28.081 --> 00:33:29.202
Master Writer identity

00:33:29.202 --> 00:33:30.482
because you think

00:33:30.561 --> 00:33:32.321
a Luanfeng Peak cultivator

00:33:32.321 --> 00:33:33.682
shouldn't do that, right?

00:33:38.161 --> 00:33:39.601
But I don't think so.

00:33:39.801 --> 00:33:41.161
I've told you before,

00:33:41.321 --> 00:33:43.202
you're a person,

00:33:43.202 --> 00:33:44.482
not a sword.

00:33:44.522 --> 00:33:45.922
You have the right to do whatever

00:33:45.922 --> 00:33:47.161
you want to do.

00:33:47.482 --> 00:33:49.242
If you still feel

00:33:49.242 --> 00:33:50.801
a bit embarrassed about it,

00:33:50.841 --> 00:33:52.801
I can help you hide

00:33:52.801 --> 00:33:54.282
your identity as Master Writer.

00:33:54.282 --> 00:33:54.801
However,

00:33:54.801 --> 00:33:56.242
you must promise me one thing.

00:33:58.161 --> 00:33:59.081
What is it?

00:33:59.801 --> 00:34:01.722
You must finish

00:34:01.722 --> 00:34:02.722
new storybooks soon.

00:34:02.722 --> 00:34:03.881
I've been waiting too long.

00:34:03.881 --> 00:34:04.962
I'm desperate to read them.

00:34:05.002 --> 00:34:06.641
If you write new storybooks,

00:34:06.641 --> 00:34:07.841
I'll help keep

00:34:07.841 --> 00:34:08.561
this secret safe.

00:34:10.641 --> 00:34:11.362
Okay.

00:34:14.906 --> 00:34:19.126
♪Stars stream in your eyes♪

00:34:19.518 --> 00:34:23.239
♪Intoxicated, I linger
and forget to return♪

00:34:23.793 --> 00:34:31.646
♪All worldly things
and gentle breezes become futile♪

00:34:31.989 --> 00:34:35.645
♪Temples await the moonlight's fall♪

00:34:35.979 --> 00:34:39.946
♪Time engraves into rings♪

00:34:40.468 --> 00:34:47.584
♪Slowly, we accompany the fading lights♪

00:34:48.613 --> 00:34:55.832
♪Slowly, we accompany the fading lights♪

00:35:10.882 --> 00:35:11.922
You almost fell.

00:35:12.882 --> 00:35:13.601
Wake up.

00:35:16.882 --> 00:35:17.601
Huan Zong,

00:35:17.681 --> 00:35:19.201
why was I lying on your lap?

00:35:22.002 --> 00:35:23.281
What's wrong with you?

00:35:24.241 --> 00:35:26.161
My legs went numb from you
lying there all night.

00:35:27.842 --> 00:35:29.042
Then let me

00:35:29.042 --> 00:35:30.442
massage them for you.

00:35:35.161 --> 00:35:35.882
No need.

00:35:37.281 --> 00:35:38.241
Why not?

00:35:40.561 --> 00:35:41.561
Because

00:35:43.721 --> 00:35:45.121
we should keep a distance.

00:35:53.201 --> 00:35:54.482
But remember this.

00:35:54.842 --> 00:35:56.121
You don't need to massage me,

00:35:56.362 --> 00:35:57.482
and never massage others.

00:35:57.601 --> 00:35:58.281
Understand?

00:35:59.601 --> 00:36:00.601
I'll remember.

00:36:02.882 --> 00:36:03.882
Where's Lin Hu?

00:36:12.402 --> 00:36:14.402
Lin Hu, you're back.

00:36:14.402 --> 00:36:16.322
Come on. Let's drink.

00:36:20.081 --> 00:36:20.761
We...

00:36:20.962 --> 00:36:21.641
We'll be

00:36:21.641 --> 00:36:23.002
friends for life,

00:36:23.002 --> 00:36:23.641
right?

00:36:25.721 --> 00:36:27.121
But I'm telling you.

00:36:27.442 --> 00:36:28.761
I can't continue today.

00:36:28.962 --> 00:36:31.241
It's time for me to sleep.

00:36:32.362 --> 00:36:34.601
Lin Hu, where are you going?

00:36:35.721 --> 00:36:36.241
Breakfast.

00:36:36.241 --> 00:36:37.322
Don't touch my seeds.

00:36:37.322 --> 00:36:39.402
Why are you taking my seeds?

00:36:40.241 --> 00:36:40.922
Give them to him.

00:36:41.081 --> 00:36:41.882
Here you go!

00:36:44.442 --> 00:36:45.962
You two, good night.

00:36:46.042 --> 00:36:47.042
- Good night.
- Good night.

00:36:50.962 --> 00:36:51.882
Huan Zong,

00:36:52.042 --> 00:36:53.922
why are you bidding him goodnight?

00:36:54.002 --> 00:36:56.161
If he sleeps
in that water vat all night,

00:36:56.241 --> 00:36:59.042
he'll definitely wake up sore tomorrow.

00:36:59.042 --> 00:37:00.042
Then he'll start yelling

00:37:00.042 --> 00:37:01.402
at us again.

00:37:01.802 --> 00:37:04.241
Foxes have flexible bodies.

00:37:04.241 --> 00:37:06.161
Sleeping in a vat won't harm him.

00:37:06.522 --> 00:37:07.802
True.

00:37:07.922 --> 00:37:08.922
Wait.

00:37:09.081 --> 00:37:10.402
He ate so many of my seeds.

00:37:10.402 --> 00:37:11.802
He finished them all.

00:37:12.042 --> 00:37:12.962
I'll buy you more.

00:37:13.281 --> 00:37:14.681
No. I don't want it.

00:37:14.802 --> 00:37:17.002
I want revenge.

00:37:19.681 --> 00:37:20.601
Look.

00:37:22.042 --> 00:37:22.761
Look!

00:37:23.161 --> 00:37:24.842
Why's this guy sleeping here?

00:37:25.641 --> 00:37:27.042
He probably did something wrong,

00:37:27.161 --> 00:37:28.561
so he was stripped by his wife

00:37:28.601 --> 00:37:29.522
and got kicked out.

00:37:29.601 --> 00:37:31.482
W-What happened?

00:37:31.482 --> 00:37:32.161
Oh, my.

00:37:32.522 --> 00:37:33.522
Are you alright?

