that I'm the best to you?

00:38:29.042 --> 00:38:31.121
Yes, yes. You are the best to me.

00:38:32.042 --> 00:38:33.121
Lin Hu.

00:38:33.442 --> 00:38:34.962
Yesterday, your young master

00:38:34.962 --> 00:38:36.962
